# TRASHBUS
 
 - GET OLD SCHOOL BUSES ALL AROUND THE COUNTRY
 - CONVERT THEM
 - FIND THE PEOPLE WHO ARE DOWN TO DO ANARCHY AND GIVE THEM THE BUS
 - FIND THE PEOPLE WHO ARE DOWN TO FUND ANARCHY AND GET THEM TO PAY FOR CONVERSIONS
- USE BUS TO DISTRIBUTE ALL THE FREE STUFF: FUEL, FOOD, CLOTHES, SERVERS, POWER,  MEDICINE, BOOKS AND SO ON
 - DIRTY KID RESCUE TEAM, PICK UP TRAVELERS STUCK ON THE ROAD
 - SHUTTLE SERVICE BETWEEN RURAL AND URBAN TRASH CAMPS
